snippet.title: Barbie Fashion Show: An Eye for Style Gameplay Nintendo DS
snippet.description:
Barbie Fashion Show: An Eye for Style Walkthrough

Let's Play - Barbie Fashion Show: An Eye for Style

ABOUT THIS GAME

Help Barbie put on fabulous fashion shows that will "WOW" the world!

With limitless customization and creative options, the possibilities are endless! From concept to catwalk, you will design the outfits and accessories for your very own fashion line. Now you can put your personal mark on the fashion world!
